WEBVTT

00:11.830 --> 00:12.510
My Queen,

00:13.350 --> 00:15.590
what are you two ladies doing?

00:15.830 --> 00:16.390
I...

00:17.480 --> 00:20.280
I'm keeping Her Majesty company
while she bathes.

00:20.760 --> 00:21.560
Your Majesty,

00:22.280 --> 00:23.670
what is going on?

00:23.670 --> 00:26.190
Is this what you wanted me to see?

00:26.960 --> 00:27.760
Your Majesty,

00:27.820 --> 00:28.780
I did hear from

00:28.810 --> 00:30.800
a maid from Her Majesty's palace who said

00:30.800 --> 00:32.540
that Her Majesty was having an affair.

00:32.540 --> 00:34.730
So I wanted you to see it for yourself.

00:35.790 --> 00:37.110
A maid

00:37.640 --> 00:39.470
said the Empress committed adultery,

00:39.470 --> 00:41.470
and you just foolishly believed it?

00:41.920 --> 00:43.520
Qinxiang, tell His Majesty.

00:43.670 --> 00:45.790
You saw Her Majesty
meeting someone secretly in the palace

00:45.790 --> 00:47.000
with your own eyes, didn't you?

00:47.000 --> 00:47.790
I didn't.

00:47.970 --> 00:49.050
I never said that.

00:53.920 --> 00:54.560
Liar!

00:55.150 --> 00:56.240
You clearly told me yourself

00:56.240 --> 00:57.750
that Her Majesty was committing adultery.

00:57.750 --> 00:59.770
I even gave you a hundred taels of silver.

00:59.770 --> 01:01.500
And now you go back on your word?

01:03.240 --> 01:04.040
Your Majesty.

02:29.540 --> 02:34.870
[REBIRTH]

02:35.240 --> 02:37.940
[Episode 16]

02:56.840 --> 02:57.640
Your Majesty,

02:58.310 --> 02:59.520
don't you remember

02:59.840 --> 03:01.470
what day it is today?

03:02.430 --> 03:05.520
Not to mention that I would
never be disloyal to you.

03:06.240 --> 03:08.870
Even if I were to do something
so unforgivable,

03:09.310 --> 03:10.960
why would I choose today of all days?

03:10.960 --> 03:13.360
Wouldn't I fear being struck by lightning?

03:28.430 --> 03:29.079
Guards.

03:29.470 --> 03:31.430
Drag Beauty Hu and this maid out

03:31.800 --> 03:33.060
and beat them to death.

03:34.840 --> 03:35.630
Your Majesty!

03:35.630 --> 03:37.240
I know I was wrong!

03:37.240 --> 03:37.870
Spare me, Your Majesty!

03:37.870 --> 03:39.240
Your Majesty, please show mercy!

03:39.240 --> 03:40.030
Drag them out!

03:40.030 --> 03:40.710
Your Majesty!

03:40.710 --> 03:41.430
Spare me, Your Majesty!

03:41.430 --> 03:44.190
Your Majesty, I was wrong!

03:44.280 --> 03:45.510
Your Majesty!

03:45.910 --> 03:48.170
-Spare me, Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

04:03.000 --> 04:05.030
You know my secret.

04:06.240 --> 04:08.000
I could kill you.

04:08.840 --> 04:10.170
Spare me, Your Majesty.

04:10.400 --> 04:12.960
I haven't seen Chu Qiao
go to hell with my own eyes yet.

04:12.960 --> 04:13.870
I can't die.

04:14.010 --> 04:15.360
Do you think this

04:16.750 --> 04:18.750
will spare your life?

04:25.240 --> 04:26.120
I did hear

04:26.120 --> 04:28.580
the conversation
between you and Lord Zhan.

04:28.850 --> 04:31.450
But what I said
is also my long-cherished wish.

04:32.070 --> 04:34.480
Back then, on my wedding day,
she and Yan Xun

04:34.480 --> 04:35.950
rebelled in Zhenhuangcheng

04:35.950 --> 04:37.750
and ruined my life's happiness.

04:38.080 --> 04:40.450
Now that I am married
to the Prince of Luo,

04:41.050 --> 04:43.480
because she resembles Princess Fu,

04:43.570 --> 04:45.300
he repeatedly comes to her aid.

04:46.120 --> 04:48.040
Your Majesty, do you remember

04:48.390 --> 04:50.240
what you said
when you agreed to my marriage

04:50.240 --> 04:51.370
to the Prince of Luo?

04:51.680 --> 04:53.870
I said I would become
your right-hand woman.

04:53.870 --> 04:55.720
I know where Chu Qiao is now.

04:56.560 --> 04:57.600
Where is she?

04:57.870 --> 04:59.200
She's gone to Lincheng.

05:00.310 --> 05:03.710
Among the prisoners exchanged
between Yan Xun and Great Yong

05:03.750 --> 05:05.630
is her Deputy Commander, He Xiao.

05:06.240 --> 05:07.440
I'm afraid right now,

05:07.750 --> 05:10.190
her hiding in Biantang as Princess Fu

05:10.560 --> 05:12.090
is already known to Yan Xun.

05:12.600 --> 05:14.930
A few days ago,
on the streets of Tangjing,

05:15.190 --> 05:17.360
I even saw a few Great Yan spies
holding her portrait,

05:17.360 --> 05:19.360
looking for her everywhere.

05:19.830 --> 05:20.830
You mean

05:21.750 --> 05:23.870
Chu Qiao went to Lincheng
while the Crown Prince

05:23.870 --> 05:24.800
was in Qiongzhou

05:25.310 --> 05:27.240
to rescue her former deputy general?

05:27.240 --> 05:27.920
Yes.

05:44.290 --> 05:46.200
I was just joking.

05:47.900 --> 05:49.330
The palace is so cold.

05:50.040 --> 05:53.310
Such a kind and lovely beauty as you.

05:53.560 --> 05:54.800
If I killed you,

05:55.750 --> 05:57.600
where could I find another?

06:12.920 --> 06:13.720
Your Majesty.

06:14.510 --> 06:15.510
So,

06:16.070 --> 06:19.400
the Crown Prince's visit
to Qiongzhou was just a diversion.

06:20.600 --> 06:23.000
Covering for Chu Qiao
to save the Xiuli Army

06:23.750 --> 06:25.750
was his real purpose.

06:36.000 --> 06:37.680
Where do you think
Princess Fu and Young Master Zhuge

06:37.680 --> 06:38.510
have gone?

06:38.720 --> 06:40.680
Why haven't they come back for dinner?

06:40.680 --> 06:43.340
-None of your business.
-None of your business.

06:43.909 --> 06:44.570
I won't eat.

06:45.180 --> 06:45.860
I won't eat.

06:48.240 --> 06:49.640
Why did you bring me here?

06:57.430 --> 06:58.360
Did you release

06:59.240 --> 07:00.370
all those lanterns?

07:03.040 --> 07:04.270
The paper on those lanterns

07:04.270 --> 07:06.910
is special madder-dyed rice paper
from Qingshan Manor.

07:06.910 --> 07:07.900
Even in strong winds,

07:07.900 --> 07:09.870
they won't easily lose
their center of gravity.

07:09.870 --> 07:12.190
So they can fly higher and farther

07:12.380 --> 07:14.140
than ordinary sky lanterns.

07:17.800 --> 07:19.270
Today isn't a festival.

07:19.560 --> 07:21.820
Why did you release so many sky lanterns?

07:22.390 --> 07:23.240
Zhuge Yue,

07:24.000 --> 07:25.120
what are you up to?

07:27.920 --> 07:28.980
These sky lanterns

07:29.310 --> 07:31.360
are not ordinary ones for blessings.

07:31.360 --> 07:34.240
They're a signal I agreed upon
with the Moon Guard of Qingshan Manor.

07:34.240 --> 07:35.840
When they see these signals,

07:35.920 --> 07:37.650
they will know I'm still alive.

07:37.920 --> 07:39.630
When we reach
the next stronghold tomorrow,

07:39.630 --> 07:41.090
they will be waiting there

07:41.510 --> 07:42.510
to meet me.

07:42.560 --> 07:45.510
You're going to contact
the Moon Guard of Qingshan Manor?

07:45.510 --> 07:46.270
Don't worry.

07:46.720 --> 07:47.940
Those who can recognize this signal

07:47.940 --> 07:49.670
are all my closest confidants.

07:49.750 --> 07:51.630
Qingshan Manor has strongholds

07:51.650 --> 07:52.920
in various countries and cities.

07:52.920 --> 07:54.680
A very small number of spies
in these strongholds

07:54.680 --> 07:56.390
are my people.

07:56.800 --> 07:58.400
I didn't contact them before

07:58.800 --> 08:00.830
because I didn't want the Zhuge family
and the Great Yong court

08:00.830 --> 08:02.390
to know I am alive,

08:02.720 --> 08:04.520
nor did I want to implicate them.

08:05.000 --> 08:06.190
But now, asking them

08:06.190 --> 08:08.650
to help me find
a few members of the Xiuli Army

08:10.190 --> 08:11.520
shouldn't be a problem.

08:16.750 --> 08:17.680
Zhuge Yue.

09:16.650 --> 09:17.790
-Greetings, Young Master Yue.
-Greetings, Young Master Yue.

09:17.790 --> 09:22.050
-Greetings, Chief of Qingshan Manor.
-Greetings, Chief of Qingshan Manor.

09:22.600 --> 09:23.510
Rise.

09:26.240 --> 09:28.570
I am no longer
the Chief of Qingshan Manor.

09:28.790 --> 09:30.250
You don't need to bow to me.

09:30.840 --> 09:31.840
Young Master Yue,

09:32.150 --> 09:34.280
we thought at Mount Ximin, you were...

09:34.370 --> 09:35.800
When we saw the sky lanterns,

09:35.800 --> 09:37.190
we couldn't believe it was true,

09:37.190 --> 09:39.460
let alone that we could see you again.

09:41.120 --> 09:42.320
Since I was away,

09:43.000 --> 09:44.360
has everything been alright?

09:44.360 --> 09:45.000
Yes.

09:45.390 --> 09:46.550
We are Moon Guard stationed

09:46.550 --> 09:48.080
at secret outposts.

09:48.270 --> 09:49.320
Since we are far from Qingshan Manor,

09:49.320 --> 09:50.030
we are fine.

09:51.210 --> 09:54.090
But we can't say for sure
about the other brothers

09:54.630 --> 09:55.830
from Qingshan Manor.

09:56.000 --> 09:57.000
Young Master Yue,

09:57.440 --> 09:59.120
when will you return to Qingshan Manor?

09:59.120 --> 10:00.050
Once you return,

10:00.120 --> 10:01.150
the brothers in Qingshan Manor

10:01.150 --> 10:05.210
won't be bullied by the young masters
of the third and fourth households.

10:06.080 --> 10:07.910
I won't return to Qingshan Manor.

10:07.910 --> 10:09.170
Why, Young Master Yue?

10:09.200 --> 10:10.820
The Zhuge family and the imperial court

10:10.820 --> 10:12.950
still don't know that I am still alive.

10:13.480 --> 10:14.630
I also hope you won't reveal

10:14.630 --> 10:15.830
that you have seen me.

10:15.840 --> 10:16.770
I came this time

10:18.150 --> 10:20.950
because I need your help
with an important matter.

10:21.150 --> 10:23.550
Help me find the remnants
of the Xiuli Army.

10:24.010 --> 10:24.700
Young Master Yue,

10:24.700 --> 10:25.910
we will do our best.

10:55.360 --> 10:56.390
Who sent you?

10:56.480 --> 10:58.880
The Crown Prince.
The Crown Prince sent me.

11:13.840 --> 11:14.790
Who are you?

11:15.150 --> 11:16.540
This is the Crown Prince's Mansion.

11:16.540 --> 11:18.340
Who dares to cause trouble here?

11:20.370 --> 11:21.170
Your Highness.

11:21.170 --> 11:22.840
Zhan Ziyu has surrounded
the outside with his men

11:22.840 --> 11:24.840
and says he wants to see King Ximeng.

11:28.390 --> 11:30.190
Lord Zhan, what brings you here?

11:42.040 --> 11:43.400
King Ximeng.

11:53.200 --> 11:54.530
By Her Majesty's order,

11:55.120 --> 11:57.670
the Crown Prince conspired
with Ximeng to assassinate His Majesty

11:57.670 --> 11:59.510
and stole Biantang's secret compendium.

11:59.510 --> 12:01.600
The Queen of Lingyue
and the fake King Ximeng

12:01.600 --> 12:03.400
are to be arrested immediately!

12:06.900 --> 12:07.540
Wait.

12:13.810 --> 12:15.870
This is the assassin
who attacked His Majesty yesterday?

12:15.870 --> 12:16.550
Yes.

12:16.840 --> 12:17.360
Lord Zuo ordered us

12:17.360 --> 12:18.930
to dispose of the body immediately

12:18.930 --> 12:19.790
without delay.

12:28.870 --> 12:32.090
[Liu's Mansion]

12:32.360 --> 12:33.600
I felt at that time

12:34.510 --> 12:38.370
that the location of the scar
on the assassin's body was very strange.

12:41.120 --> 12:43.630
It seemed to be deliberately
hiding something.

12:43.630 --> 12:45.000
So I took a closer look

12:45.200 --> 12:46.960
and found that at the edge of the outline,

12:46.960 --> 12:48.630
it was originally a tattoo.

12:49.440 --> 12:51.320
The last time I saw a tattoo
on the back of someone's neck

12:51.320 --> 12:52.550
was 15 years ago

12:53.030 --> 12:55.490
when I led troops
to wipe out the Nanxi Tribe.

12:55.960 --> 12:57.270
Fifteen years ago,

12:57.270 --> 12:59.510
Biantang exterminated the Nanxi people.

12:59.510 --> 13:01.600
Even if someone
was lucky enough to escape,

13:01.600 --> 13:03.390
how could they work for the Crown Prince?

13:03.390 --> 13:05.720
Someone must be framing the Crown Prince!

13:07.030 --> 13:08.440
Please say something!

13:10.810 --> 13:13.010
The Crown Prince is the heir of Biantang

13:13.670 --> 13:16.270
and His Majesty's
only legitimate bloodline.

13:16.720 --> 13:18.960
Why would he collude with Ximeng

13:18.960 --> 13:20.890
to commit patricide and regicide?

13:22.890 --> 13:24.130
And that assassin.

13:25.080 --> 13:27.200
Without any preparation,

13:27.200 --> 13:29.670
he infiltrated the palace
late at night to assassinate the Emperor.

13:29.670 --> 13:34.080
He confessed at once
to acting on the Crown Prince's orders,

13:34.080 --> 13:36.010
then killed himself immediately.

13:36.320 --> 13:39.320
This series of actions
is full of suspicious points.

13:39.670 --> 13:41.670
Do you think no one in the court

13:42.000 --> 13:43.790
can see through it?

13:49.200 --> 13:50.360
You mean...

13:50.630 --> 13:52.360
This is a messy business,

13:52.510 --> 13:54.570
and the Emperor's own family affair.

13:54.630 --> 13:58.150
None of us—you, the officials, or I—
may intervene.

13:58.390 --> 14:00.840
Go back and write a leave request now,

14:00.840 --> 14:02.030
saying you are sick.

14:02.030 --> 14:03.870
Stay quietly in your mansion.

14:04.320 --> 14:05.780
Don't come out and meddle.

14:06.200 --> 14:07.960
And don't come to me.

14:09.510 --> 14:11.150
I will continue to be sick.

14:11.150 --> 14:12.360
Go back quickly.

14:34.200 --> 14:35.320
Your Majesty,

14:36.000 --> 14:37.790
His Majesty's injuries are not serious.

14:37.790 --> 14:39.360
They are just superficial wounds.

14:39.360 --> 14:40.720
He will recover in a few days.

14:40.720 --> 14:42.360
But it's been so many days.

14:43.220 --> 14:45.280
Why is His Majesty still unconscious

14:45.930 --> 14:48.290
and delirious?

14:49.270 --> 14:50.080
Well...

14:58.600 --> 14:59.480
Your Majesty.

14:59.960 --> 15:02.320
His Majesty has old ailments.

15:02.670 --> 15:04.350
He has overworked himself daily,

15:04.350 --> 15:05.960
exhausting too much energy.

15:06.420 --> 15:09.990
Coupled with excessive eating
and drinking,

15:10.240 --> 15:11.790
this has caused extreme anxiety

15:11.790 --> 15:13.120
and an irregular pulse.

15:13.120 --> 15:13.920
I'm afraid...

15:14.400 --> 15:15.320
Afraid of what?

15:15.910 --> 15:18.120
I'm afraid even with good care,

15:18.120 --> 15:20.250
it will be hard to recover to how it was.

15:54.030 --> 15:56.270
[Crown Prince Maocheng]

15:55.440 --> 15:56.720
You are finally here.

16:03.210 --> 16:04.810
You've hidden your true self

16:05.530 --> 16:07.330
and endured for all these years.

16:07.960 --> 16:09.160
It's been hard on you.

16:10.000 --> 16:11.550
What you've always coveted

16:12.600 --> 16:15.000
is the throne I sit upon, right?

16:15.720 --> 16:17.600
Stop deceiving yourself.

16:18.080 --> 16:20.000
You and the Prince of Chang
are from the same mother,

16:20.000 --> 16:21.750
the legitimate flesh and blood of Mother.

16:21.750 --> 16:22.440
While I am,

16:23.330 --> 16:24.490
in your eyes,

16:25.120 --> 16:26.520
just an illegitimate son

16:27.080 --> 16:28.750
born to a lady

16:29.360 --> 16:30.960
of low status.

16:31.910 --> 16:35.200
If I hadn't fought my way
into Xuri Palace today,

16:35.630 --> 16:38.600
it wouldn't have been long
before you got rid of me,

16:40.670 --> 16:43.600
just like how you got rid of
your so-called brothers!

16:45.030 --> 16:47.490
Murdering your brother
to seize the throne,

16:48.200 --> 16:50.150
you will be cursed by heaven!

17:46.830 --> 17:48.110
Why haven't I

17:49.240 --> 17:50.680
seen you in the mansion?

17:51.110 --> 17:53.960
Although you haven't seen me,
Your Highness,

17:54.510 --> 17:58.440
I have long admired you.

18:00.370 --> 18:02.940
Each time you visited
the Crown Prince's Mansion

18:02.940 --> 18:05.540
to discuss affairs,
I would secretly watch you

18:05.830 --> 18:07.070
from the festooned gate
in the west courtyard,

18:07.070 --> 18:10.340
as you walked from the palace gate
to the Crown Prince's study.

18:10.340 --> 18:11.860
I just never thought

18:13.440 --> 18:14.510
I would see your heroic bearing

18:14.510 --> 18:15.880
in such a way.

18:21.790 --> 18:23.350
Do you think by saying this,

18:23.960 --> 18:25.350
I will spare you?

18:26.200 --> 18:27.270
No! No!

18:27.860 --> 18:28.450
Let go!

18:29.000 --> 18:29.690
Let go!

18:32.350 --> 18:33.070
Your Highness,

18:33.070 --> 18:34.160
starting today,

18:34.720 --> 18:36.780
you are the Crown Prince of Biantang.

18:36.790 --> 18:39.830
I am willing to serve by your side.

18:40.590 --> 18:41.450
Your Highness!

18:43.790 --> 18:44.650
Your Highness!

18:44.700 --> 18:46.430
I am willing to give up any status

18:46.430 --> 18:47.820
to serve by your side.

19:11.250 --> 19:13.450
I can let you continue to be a concubine

19:15.620 --> 19:19.090
and be the most honorable woman
in Biantang!

19:21.920 --> 19:23.860
[Yuelai Inn]

19:36.580 --> 19:37.890
-General Chu!
-General Chu!

19:37.890 --> 19:40.550
I'm Li Ben,
First-Class Scout of the Xiuli Army,

19:40.640 --> 19:42.370
reporting to you, General Chu!

19:43.030 --> 19:45.270
I'm Xia Qingjiang,
Outpost of the Xiuli Army,

19:45.270 --> 19:46.590
reporting to you, General Chu!

19:46.590 --> 19:48.160
I'm a Corporal of the Infantry Battalion
of the Xiuli Army,

19:48.160 --> 19:49.750
reporting to you, General Chu!

19:49.750 --> 19:51.270
I'm He Shao, Archer of the Xiuli Army,

19:51.270 --> 19:52.790
reporting to you, General Chu!

19:52.790 --> 19:55.030
I'm Lang Li, Deputy Commander
of Xiuli Army's Infantry Battalion,

19:55.030 --> 19:56.400
reporting to you, General Chu!

19:56.400 --> 19:57.680
I'm He Xiao,

19:58.270 --> 19:59.400
Deputy Commander of the Xiuli Army,

19:59.400 --> 20:01.130
reporting to you, General Chu!

20:03.400 --> 20:04.110
Good.

20:04.680 --> 20:05.960
You are all alive.

20:06.880 --> 20:08.110
That's great.

20:08.750 --> 20:09.840
We are alive.

20:10.590 --> 20:12.880
Young Master Zhuge sent people to find us.

20:12.880 --> 20:14.830
Back then, I couldn't save you in time

20:14.830 --> 20:16.160
and made you suffer.

20:16.480 --> 20:17.740
How could we blame you?

20:17.830 --> 20:19.640
It was Cheng Yuan who deceived us.

20:19.640 --> 20:20.300
-Yes!
-Yes!

20:20.930 --> 20:22.410
He Xiao told me.

20:23.240 --> 20:24.510
Out of 5,000 brothers,

20:25.640 --> 20:27.120
only you guys are left.

20:33.440 --> 20:35.170
I am a general of the Xiuli Army.

20:35.240 --> 20:37.040
5,200 soldiers of the Xiuli Army

20:37.350 --> 20:38.640
shall be brought home,

20:39.680 --> 20:41.160
whether alive or dead.

20:46.350 --> 20:49.240
There are 5,200 soldiers
in the Xiuli Army in total.

20:49.950 --> 20:50.780
Most of them

20:51.270 --> 20:52.830
died on the battlefield.

20:53.110 --> 20:55.920
Among the thousands
who were not buried in Great Yan,

20:55.920 --> 20:57.160
excluding those who returned home,

20:56.180 --> 20:59.040
[The Loyal Martyrs of the Xiuli Army]

20:57.270 --> 20:58.880
the rest are all here.

20:59.640 --> 21:00.880
Many of the fallen

21:01.750 --> 21:03.240
could not be found.

21:03.880 --> 21:05.590
I collected their belongings

21:06.270 --> 21:08.670
and buried them together in this cenotaph.

21:30.440 --> 21:31.110
Wang Jin.

21:32.920 --> 21:34.320
Wang Jin was from Bizhou,

21:35.160 --> 21:36.680
whose family grew peaches.

21:36.680 --> 21:39.410
When we were in the army,
whenever he missed home,

21:39.550 --> 21:41.480
he wanted to eat the yellow peaches
from Bizhou.

21:41.480 --> 21:42.110
Brother,

21:42.400 --> 21:44.200
I'll put the yellow peaches
from your hometown here for you.

21:44.200 --> 21:46.150
If you want to eat them,
just tell me in my dream,

21:46.150 --> 21:47.610
and I'll bring them to you.

21:50.920 --> 21:51.680
Chen Yuan.

21:52.130 --> 21:53.590
Chen Yuan was an opera fan.

21:53.940 --> 21:55.340
He didn't finish reading

21:55.680 --> 21:57.160
the ending of this chapbook.

21:57.160 --> 21:58.960
I'm afraid
he won't be able to rest in peace.

21:58.960 --> 21:59.640
Brother,

22:00.350 --> 22:01.610
I'll burn this for you.

22:02.790 --> 22:03.990
I hope you can be happy

22:05.070 --> 22:06.200
in the world beyond.

22:17.310 --> 22:18.030
Brothers!

22:19.000 --> 22:20.460
They died for our country.

22:20.550 --> 22:21.950
They risked their lives,

22:22.790 --> 22:24.160
which is admirable.

22:24.920 --> 22:27.310
See off the soldiers!

22:27.720 --> 22:30.250
-See off the soldiers!
-See off the soldiers!

22:34.400 --> 22:36.930
-See off the soldiers!
-See off the soldiers!

22:38.410 --> 22:42.350
♪ Wind sighs bleakly ♪

22:42.380 --> 22:44.860
♪ Yi River cold ♪

22:45.380 --> 22:48.800
♪ A warrior goes ♪

22:45.830 --> 22:46.790
Brothers,

22:48.110 --> 22:49.270
may you rest in peace!

22:48.820 --> 22:51.610
♪ Never to return ♪

22:52.240 --> 22:55.530
♪ Flames of war arise ♪

22:55.560 --> 22:58.110
♪ Golden spears and steeds ♪

22:59.010 --> 23:02.330
♪ Swords flash, and shadows dance ♪

23:02.360 --> 23:07.110
♪ Blood dyes the yellow sand ♪

23:07.140 --> 23:09.550
♪ Through woe and weal ♪

23:10.390 --> 23:13.260
♪ We shared adversity ♪

23:13.940 --> 23:16.080
♪ Heart to heart and soul to soul ♪

23:16.100 --> 23:20.780
♪ Loyalty beyond all price ♪

23:36.390 --> 23:39.760
♪ Loyal souls forever dwell ♪

23:39.790 --> 23:42.940
♪ Heaven and earth mourn together ♪

23:43.270 --> 23:46.440
♪ A tragic epic ♪

23:46.460 --> 23:49.900
♪ Shall stand through all ages ♪

23:50.030 --> 23:53.520
♪ Loyal souls forever dwell ♪

23:53.550 --> 23:56.710
♪ Heaven and earth mourn together ♪

23:56.930 --> 23:59.960
♪ A tragic epic ♪

24:00.310 --> 24:04.210
♪ Shall stand through all ages ♪

24:28.750 --> 24:30.080
There's no one here now.

24:30.790 --> 24:31.830
Cry if you want.

24:32.400 --> 24:33.590
No one will see you.

24:35.830 --> 24:36.920
Who wants to cry?

24:50.420 --> 24:51.220
Zhuge Yue,

24:53.200 --> 24:54.030
thank you.

24:58.710 --> 25:00.510
Ahead is the border of Biantang.

25:01.550 --> 25:03.070
Lady Chu and Young Master Zhuge ordered

25:03.070 --> 25:04.030
us to split up.

25:04.030 --> 25:05.550
I'll take the Xiuli Army north.

25:05.550 --> 25:06.880
You follow Lady Chu east

25:06.880 --> 25:07.880
back to Tangjing.

25:08.240 --> 25:10.590
Have you arranged a place to stay?

25:11.400 --> 25:13.000
Our young master has arranged it.

25:13.000 --> 25:14.960
When he was carrying out
a mission in his early years,

25:14.960 --> 25:17.270
he bought a villa
in the territory of Biantang.

25:17.270 --> 25:19.000
I will take Lord He and the Xiuli Army

25:19.000 --> 25:20.200
to settle down first.

25:20.510 --> 25:22.400
That place is not far from Tangjing.

25:22.400 --> 25:23.270
If necessary,

25:23.510 --> 25:24.910
we can assist at any time.

25:31.160 --> 25:32.090
Why are you here?

25:32.400 --> 25:33.430
Something happened in Tangjing.

25:33.430 --> 25:35.030
The Crown Prince was accused
of assassinating the Emperor

25:35.030 --> 25:36.160
and colluding with King Ximeng.

25:36.160 --> 25:37.400
He was put into prison by the Empress.

25:37.400 --> 25:39.440
Our restaurant was also sealed up.

25:39.510 --> 25:40.910
The Princess has set off.

25:42.070 --> 25:45.470
The Ximeng mission
has all been arrested and put into prison.

25:45.590 --> 25:48.710
The Queen of Lingyue
and the fake King Ximeng were not caught.

25:48.710 --> 25:49.360
However,

25:50.240 --> 25:51.790
the Queen of Lingyue's personal guards

25:51.790 --> 25:52.960
have all confessed.

25:53.160 --> 25:55.430
The ones who helped them
get the compendium

25:55.430 --> 25:57.350
are the Crown Prince and Chu Qiao.

25:59.630 --> 26:01.830
These witnesses and physical evidence

26:02.240 --> 26:05.700
are enough to prove
the Crown Prince's collusion with Ximeng.

26:12.860 --> 26:14.070
Sir, your water is ready.

26:14.070 --> 26:14.720
Thank you.

26:19.570 --> 26:21.640
We are taking the fastest route
to Tangjing.

26:21.640 --> 26:22.700
We have to go through
the mountains all the way.

26:22.700 --> 26:24.350
The horses definitely can't bear it.

26:24.350 --> 26:25.350
But I have arranged for the Moon Guard

26:25.350 --> 26:26.750
to wait in the town ahead.

26:27.160 --> 26:29.240
As long as we go down the mountain,
we can change to new horses.

26:29.240 --> 26:30.240
We will travel day and night,

26:30.240 --> 26:31.640
cross the mountain from Liu River,

26:31.640 --> 26:32.970
and arrive earlier than

26:33.120 --> 26:34.270
Minglu's team.

26:34.680 --> 26:36.630
You really are the military counselor
of Great Yong.

26:36.630 --> 26:39.360
You are so familiar
with the terrain of Biantang.

26:42.240 --> 26:42.960
Yes.

26:43.680 --> 26:45.440
So if Li Ce takes you away,

26:45.870 --> 26:48.000
I will definitely not spare Biantang.

26:49.740 --> 26:50.430
Let's go.

27:04.070 --> 27:06.310
[Li Qi, General of Cavalry of Biantang]

27:12.790 --> 27:14.950
General Li was assassinated
the night before last.

27:14.950 --> 27:15.680
He survived,

27:15.770 --> 27:17.590
but the assassin cut off one of his hands.

27:17.590 --> 27:19.510
We received this box the next day,

27:19.590 --> 27:20.920
along with this letter.

27:23.920 --> 27:25.320
Present the letter to me.

27:52.250 --> 27:53.910
Your Majesty, this letter...

27:57.920 --> 27:59.920
Yan Xun sent his men to deliver this.

28:00.720 --> 28:03.250
He already knows
that Chu Qiao is in Biantang.

28:04.340 --> 28:07.200
He wants us to hand over
the Queen of Great Yan to him.

28:07.400 --> 28:08.240
Otherwise...

28:08.880 --> 28:09.830
Otherwise what?

28:10.240 --> 28:11.590
Otherwise, his Black Eagle Army

28:11.590 --> 28:14.650
will break through
Biantang's northern defense line.

28:16.900 --> 28:19.000
[Qifeng Palace]

28:18.060 --> 28:19.780
Yan Xun is so audacious.

28:19.960 --> 28:21.840
Our two Generals of Cavalry in Biantang

28:21.840 --> 28:23.270
are Sun Di and Li Qi.

28:23.880 --> 28:25.750
He actually, so quietly,

28:25.750 --> 28:27.080
cut off one of his hands.

28:27.680 --> 28:30.030
He also cut off one of Biantang's arms!

28:30.920 --> 28:31.720
Your Majesty.

28:32.510 --> 28:33.110
That Chu Qiao

28:33.110 --> 28:34.670
has always been a great threat to us.

28:34.670 --> 28:36.240
Why don't we take this opportunity

28:36.240 --> 28:37.510
to issue a warrant for her arrest

28:37.510 --> 28:38.720
and return her to Great Yan,

28:38.720 --> 28:40.450
to eliminate future troubles?

28:41.360 --> 28:42.080
Fool!

28:42.510 --> 28:43.750
If we hand over Chu Qiao now,

28:43.750 --> 28:46.510
it means we admit to harboring
the Queen of Great Yan.

28:46.510 --> 28:48.430
If Yan Xun wants to use this as an excuse

28:48.430 --> 28:51.300
to attack our northern defenses,

28:52.070 --> 28:54.590
at that time,
Biantang will be in the wrong,

28:54.690 --> 28:58.220
and we won't know how to conduct ourselves
among other nations!

29:00.520 --> 29:01.250
I am foolish.

29:01.790 --> 29:03.650
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

29:04.870 --> 29:05.670
Your Majesty.

29:08.110 --> 29:08.790
What is it?

29:09.410 --> 29:10.920
The Princess Consort of Luo is outside.

29:10.920 --> 29:12.750
She says she has news
about the new King of Great Yan

29:12.750 --> 29:14.550
and wants to discuss it with you.

29:16.030 --> 29:16.960
What did you say?

29:18.310 --> 29:19.030
I said,

29:19.510 --> 29:21.350
Biantang and Great Yan
should form a marriage alliance

29:21.350 --> 29:22.920
by marrying off Princess Fu.

29:22.920 --> 29:23.550
Right now,

29:24.000 --> 29:26.510
Yan Xun has known
that Chu Qiao is in Biantang.

29:26.510 --> 29:27.970
If you don't hand her over,

29:28.030 --> 29:29.110
given his character,

29:29.110 --> 29:30.770
he definitely won't let it go.

29:30.830 --> 29:32.350
If he uses this to attack Biantang,

29:32.350 --> 29:34.200
even if Biantang's military strength
is not inferior to Great Yan's,

29:34.200 --> 29:35.960
it would still be an unprovoked disaster.

29:35.960 --> 29:37.440
But if you hand her over,

29:38.150 --> 29:39.680
it will amount to admitting

29:39.750 --> 29:41.830
that Biantang harbored
the Queen of Great Yan.

29:41.830 --> 29:43.880
Even if Yan Xun
is willing not to pursue it,

29:43.880 --> 29:45.860
Biantang will not only be humiliated

29:45.860 --> 29:48.060
but also lose General Li Qi for nothing.

29:48.590 --> 29:50.880
How could you let it go?

29:51.970 --> 29:54.920
But under the pretense of
marrying Princess Fu to form an alliance,

29:54.920 --> 29:57.320
we can confirm her identity
as the Princess

29:57.680 --> 29:59.270
and send Chu Qiao away.

29:59.510 --> 30:00.550
We can also ask Great Yan

30:00.550 --> 30:02.280
for a generous betrothal gift,

30:02.490 --> 30:04.450
such as horses, gold, silver,

30:04.480 --> 30:06.130
or even cities in Great Yan.

30:06.470 --> 30:07.880
Yan Xun will give

30:08.260 --> 30:09.830
whatever you want.

30:10.390 --> 30:12.260
But where Chu Qiao is right now

30:12.510 --> 30:13.640
is still unknown.

30:14.110 --> 30:16.760
The news of the Crown Prince's
imprisonment has spread.

30:16.760 --> 30:19.440
She must be on her way back to Tangjing.

30:22.640 --> 30:25.120
This was your idea?

30:26.350 --> 30:29.480
Are you willing
to let Yan Xun marry Princess Fu

30:30.200 --> 30:31.830
to be the Queen of Great Yan?

30:32.720 --> 30:35.070
Since I'm already
the Princess Consort of Luo of Biantang,

30:35.070 --> 30:37.870
I naturally only
have the Prince of Luo in my heart.

30:38.160 --> 30:40.350
But I dare not deceive you, Your Majesty.

30:40.350 --> 30:42.510
I grew up with Yan Xun from childhood,

30:42.720 --> 30:44.880
and we do have some childhood friendship.

30:44.880 --> 30:46.810
I am willing to use this friendship

30:46.840 --> 30:49.440
to facilitate this marriage alliance
for you.

30:54.920 --> 30:56.160
His Majesty is coming back.

30:56.160 --> 30:58.070
Prepare everything in advance.

30:59.750 --> 31:01.680
All the desks and screens

31:01.790 --> 31:03.310
must be wiped clean one by one.

31:03.310 --> 31:04.720
Keep the tea warm.

31:05.440 --> 31:06.110
And...

31:06.480 --> 31:07.400
My Lady,

31:07.400 --> 31:08.800
I was just in the court...

31:18.950 --> 31:20.070
I was just in the court

31:20.070 --> 31:21.930
and heard the elders discussing.

31:22.350 --> 31:23.440
They say

31:24.620 --> 31:26.420
His Majesty has gone to Biantang

31:26.640 --> 31:28.030
and might not return for a while.

31:28.030 --> 31:30.090
Why has His Majesty gone to Biantang?

31:30.550 --> 31:31.440
I heard...

31:33.160 --> 31:34.760
that Chu Qiao is in Biantang.

31:37.430 --> 31:40.890
Prince of Luo Li Yan, legitimate son
of the late Prince of Chang,

31:40.890 --> 31:43.350
is loyal, filial, and well-mannered,
possessing extraordinary literary talent.

31:43.350 --> 31:45.350
He is hereby appointed Minister of Rites

31:45.350 --> 31:48.000
and granted a mansion of 500 qing
and 100 jade belts.

31:48.000 --> 31:52.310
He's ordered to negotiate peace
and marriage with the King of Great Yan.

32:05.160 --> 32:06.030
Your Highness,

32:06.310 --> 32:08.030
you should properly thank
the Princess Consort of Luo

32:08.030 --> 32:09.590
for securing this position for you.

32:09.590 --> 32:10.440
From now on,

32:10.440 --> 32:12.450
you are no longer an idle prince,

32:12.550 --> 32:14.880
but the Minister of Rites.

32:40.920 --> 32:41.880
Perfect timing.

32:42.740 --> 32:45.950
Help me see which hairpin looks better.

32:47.790 --> 32:48.480
Chun'er.

32:49.350 --> 32:51.470
You've been going to the palace
a lot lately,

32:51.470 --> 32:53.270
getting so close to Her Majesty.

32:53.790 --> 32:55.600
Then Her Majesty suddenly rewarded me

32:55.600 --> 32:57.640
and put me in charge of
some political marriage.

32:57.640 --> 32:58.970
What exactly did you do?

32:59.920 --> 33:00.830
Strange.

33:01.640 --> 33:03.240
I've done so much for you.

33:03.510 --> 33:05.570
Why are you thanking me in such a tone?

33:06.890 --> 33:07.680
Tell me,

33:07.900 --> 33:09.530
what exactly did you do?

33:17.640 --> 33:18.400
Me?

33:19.350 --> 33:21.350
I did many great things for you.

33:22.030 --> 33:22.790
First, I told

33:22.790 --> 33:24.880
the spy Yan Xun sent to find Chu Qiao

33:25.070 --> 33:26.590
that Princess Fu

33:26.590 --> 33:28.720
is the Queen of Great Yan
they are looking for.

33:28.720 --> 33:30.070
Then I told Her Majesty

33:30.350 --> 33:31.880
that Chu Qiao is not in Tangjing,

33:31.880 --> 33:34.680
but went to Lincheng
to find her old subordinates.

33:35.960 --> 33:36.880
Tell me,

33:37.720 --> 33:39.520
now that Her Majesty knows this,

33:39.650 --> 33:41.980
how could she not be burning with anxiety?

33:44.920 --> 33:46.480
But this is not enough.

33:47.640 --> 33:49.360
The greatest merit I achieved

33:49.830 --> 33:52.430
is to think of a foolproof plan
for Her Majesty.

33:54.310 --> 33:56.710
I told her to marry Chu Qiao off
to Great Yan,

33:57.200 --> 34:00.200
using Princess Fu's name
for the political marriage.

34:00.550 --> 34:01.880
Her Majesty was so happy

34:02.480 --> 34:05.480
that she appointed you
as the envoy for this marriage.

34:06.810 --> 34:09.070
You want me to negotiate
with the King of Great Yan

34:09.070 --> 34:10.870
for the marriage of Princess Fu?

34:11.880 --> 34:13.280
Why did you do this?

34:16.840 --> 34:18.190
Chun'er, Chun'er,

34:18.210 --> 34:19.170
don't do this!

34:23.290 --> 34:24.409
You ask me why?

34:25.190 --> 34:26.590
Because I'm not like you.

34:26.880 --> 34:29.340
You only swallow insults
and wait for death.

34:29.400 --> 34:30.630
You dare not fight for anything.

34:30.630 --> 34:32.230
You only use high-sounding reasons

34:32.230 --> 34:33.360
to deceive yourself and others,

34:33.360 --> 34:34.400
saying you don't want it

34:34.400 --> 34:35.480
and staying away from disputes.

34:35.480 --> 34:36.570
It's just because you don't dare!

34:36.570 --> 34:37.170
Chun'er,

34:38.480 --> 34:40.159
is that how you see me?

34:40.630 --> 34:41.320
Yes!

34:41.980 --> 34:44.110
In my eyes, you are just that cowardly.

34:44.510 --> 34:46.400
You like me and married me,

34:46.630 --> 34:48.360
but don't even dare to touch me.

34:48.670 --> 34:49.230
And you say

34:49.230 --> 34:51.360
you'll wait until the day I'm willing.

34:51.920 --> 34:52.800
Let me tell you,

34:53.000 --> 34:54.480
that day will never come.

34:54.480 --> 34:55.920
I will never willingly

34:55.920 --> 34:57.530
love a cowardly and incompetent person!

34:57.530 --> 34:58.400
I'm not!

35:18.780 --> 35:20.780
According to Her Majesty's decree,

35:21.630 --> 35:22.360
Princess Fu

35:23.280 --> 35:24.540
is virtuous, elegant,

35:24.960 --> 35:26.320
gentle, and wise.

35:27.070 --> 35:29.960
To show Her Majesty's favor and regard,

35:30.710 --> 35:33.370
she is specially granted
to marry into Great Yan

35:33.630 --> 35:36.230
to form a good relationship
between the two countries.

35:36.230 --> 35:39.710
This dowry is a gift from Her Majesty.

35:52.610 --> 35:53.410
Interesting.

35:53.590 --> 35:57.320
The envoy sent by Biantang even brought
his female family members.

36:00.980 --> 36:02.190
Greetings, King of Great Yan,

36:02.190 --> 36:03.150
My Lord.

36:03.510 --> 36:04.440
The Prince of Luo said

36:04.440 --> 36:06.020
our Princess Consort
is an old acquaintance of yours,

36:06.020 --> 36:07.360
so there's no need for formalities.

36:07.360 --> 36:08.110
Please move

36:08.110 --> 36:09.760
to the itinerant court,
prepared for you, to talk.

36:09.760 --> 36:13.070
Your Princess Consort
is an old acquaintance of mine?

36:41.670 --> 36:42.670
Your Majesty,

36:43.150 --> 36:44.210
congratulations.

36:44.250 --> 36:45.160
Why is it you?

36:45.510 --> 36:48.510
Prince of Luo Li Yan
is the Empress-appointed Marriage Envoy.

36:48.510 --> 36:50.840
He is here to welcome
the King of Great Yan.

36:51.320 --> 36:53.050
I am Li Yan's Princess Consort,

36:53.360 --> 36:55.960
and I also came with him
by Her Majesty's order.

36:56.230 --> 36:58.890
It is hoped that you
can abandon past prejudices

36:59.590 --> 37:02.520
and facilitate the marriage
and our good relations.

37:02.690 --> 37:04.730
Do you not want it?

37:06.760 --> 37:10.290
Marrying Princess Fu
is the most important matter in Great Yan.

37:10.730 --> 37:12.080
Since you've let it go,

37:12.300 --> 37:13.970
how could I keep it in mind?

37:17.100 --> 37:19.310
Then, please move to the itinerant court

37:19.310 --> 37:21.660
to discuss the marriage alliance with us.

37:45.700 --> 37:47.580
I just want to see you
suffer with my own eyes,

37:47.580 --> 37:49.280
watching you lose everything,

37:49.280 --> 37:51.280
including everyone you care about!

37:51.880 --> 37:53.340
I'll make every single one

37:53.500 --> 37:54.270
of them

37:54.610 --> 37:56.900
live a life worse than death.

37:57.110 --> 37:58.640
It's just that besides him,

37:58.800 --> 38:00.590
there is another group of people.

38:00.590 --> 38:01.280
-Marriage alliance?
-Marriage alliance?

38:01.280 --> 38:03.680
It's just that I am the Princess's guard,

38:03.800 --> 38:04.750
and I also have

38:04.840 --> 38:06.820
some personal relationship with her,

38:06.820 --> 38:08.210
so it is inconvenient to leave easily.
